  "text": "Other cell surface markers, such as several chemokines and urokinase plasminogen activator (uPA) and its receptor, uPAR (CD87), have been found in SCLC, co-express CD44 and the MDR1 drug resistance gene [CITATION_1] . The role of these proteins in contributing to lung cancer is not known.",
